New in the editor: a Resize tool with cleanEdge smart resampling for scaling your art, and a one-tap Precision toggle. You can now delete your account from inside the app (Profile → Settings). Comments removed by moderators show as tombstones, and artwork grids display non-square art properly letterboxed. Under the hood: major memory hardening — enormous animations can no longer crash the app; drawings now stop growing at a safe size with a clear warning instead. Thanks for testing Makapix Club!
